           &kp NUMBER_1  &kp NUMBER_2  &kp NUMBER_3  &kp NUMBER_4  &kp N5    &kp MINUS  &kp PLUS        &kp EQUAL        &kp ASTERISK  &kp CARET
&kp GRAVE  &kp NUMBER_6  &kp N7        &kp N8        &kp N9        &kp N0    &kp UNDER  &kp LEFT_BRACE  &kp RIGHT_BRACE  &kp AMPS      &kp PIPE     &kp BACKSLASH
